Hello.

17:35.934 --> 17:37.726
<i>Hey Dad.</i>

17:38.814 --> 17:40.638
Anthony, is that you?

17:41.981 --> 17:43.550
<i>Yeah.</i>

17:44.510 --> 17:46.942
I haven't heard
from you in a while.

17:48.447 --> 17:52.926
<i>Yeah, sorry
about that, I've been busy.</i>

17:54.525 --> 17:55.998
What do you want?

17:58.078 --> 18:00.031
<i>I'm just calling
to see how you are.</i>

18:00.350 --> 18:01.789
Oh cut the crap, Anthony,

18:01.791 --> 18:03.807
I didn't come down with
yesterday's fall of shit.

18:07.647 --> 18:09.279
<i>Dad?</i>

18:10.814 --> 18:12.702
<i>They're gonna kill me.</i>

